OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FAston Martin has cut 170 jobs after
OL,7,Flosses widened by a fifth last year
OL,8,Fand a slump in sales.
OL,10,FThe luxury car manufacturer - famous
OL,11,Ffor making fictional spy James Bond's
OL,12,Fcars - said it is planning to axe 5%
OL,13,Fof its workforce as part of a cost-
OL,14,Fcutting plan.
OL,16,FIt is understood to be making most of
OL,17,Fthe cuts - about 150 people - in the
OL,18,FUK.
