OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FAll of the company's departments will
OL,7,Fbe hit, including manufacturing,
OL,8,Foffice jobs and management.
OL,10,FAston Martin has its headquarters in
OL,11,FGaydon, Warwickshire, and another
OL,12,Ffactory in St Athan, South Wales.
OL,14,FIt said on Wednesday that the aim is
OL,15,Fto make sure the company is
OL,16,F"appropriately resourced for its
OL,17,Ffuture plans", calling the cuts a
OL,18,F"difficult but necessary action".
