OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FThe company is targeting yearly
OL,7,Fsavings of #25 million, and expects to
OL,8,Fhit about half of that total this year.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Aston Martin also said it
OL,11,Fwill delay the rollout of its first
OL,12,Ffully electric vehicle until near the
OL,13,Fend of the decade.
OL,15,FIt was originally set to be launched
OL,16,Fin 2026, and the delay is part of what
OL,17,Fthe company is calling a "phased
OL,18,Fapproach" to electrification.
