OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FSince it was bought by Canadian
OL,7,Fbillionaire Lawrence Stroll in 2020,
OL,8,FAston Martin has pushed on with a
OL,9,Fswathe of new model launches in a bid
OL,10,Fto turn its ailing fortunes around.
OL,12,FIt recently appointed Adrian Hallmark
OL,13,Fas its new chief executive, with him
OL,14,Ftaking on the role in September amid a
OL,15,Framping up of sales of its new Vantage
OL,16,Fand DBX707 models, which it said
OL,17,Fhelped boost production volumes.
OL,19,FThe company also launched its flagship
OL,20,FVanquish model in September.
