OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FAston Martin said the launches helped
OL,7,Fboost sales later in the year as it
OL,8,Fstarted delivering more of the new
OL,9,Fmodels to customers, with wholesale
OL,10,Fvolumes picking up 10% year on year in
OL,11,Fthe second half compared with 2023.
OL,13,FBut the company's wholesale volumes
OL,14,Ffor the whole year were still down 9%
OL,15,Fat 6,030 cars, pushing its pre-tax
OL,16,Flosses to gape by a further 21% to
OL,17,F#289 million.
