OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FIt also saw its debt pile balloon by
OL,7,F43% to #1.16 billion during the year,
OL,8,Fwhile shares were down about 33% over
OL,9,Fthe last year.
OL,11,FAston Martin had warned in September
OL,12,Fthat supply chain issues would hit
OL,13,Fannual production by about 1,000 cars.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, it has also been battling
OL,16,Fweak trading in China amid a downturn
OL,17,Fin demand across the country.
