OL,3,CAston Martin cuts 170 jobs after slump
OL,4,Cin sales
OL,6,FMr Hallmark said it has been "a period
OL,7,Fof intense product launches, coupled
OL,8,Fwith industry-wide and company
OL,9,Fchallenges".
OL,11,FHe said he wants Aston Martin to
OL,12,F"transition from a high-potential
OL,13,Fbusiness to a high-performing one,
OL,14,Fbetter equipped to navigate future
OL,15,Fopportunities and uncertainties".
